sect1.title: External Interfaces
sect1.para:
The external interfaces of ErrHdl_MQb are described by the Component Diagram "Interfaces" in the SWA at the following location in Enterprise Architect: VW_ICAS1.Chorus_6M.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.ErrHdl_MQB.SW Architecture.Static.Interfaces.
A part of the external interfaces used by Error Handler is provided by the component "RTE Light" and includes generated interfaces which are based on the SST_ERRHDL_MQB SST files.

sect1.title: External Dependencies
sect1.para: The external dependencies of ErrHdl_MQB are described by the Component Diagram "Dependencies" in the SWA at the following location in Enterprise Architect: VW_ICAS1.Chorus_6M.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.ErrHdl_MQB.SW Architecture.Static.Dependencies
